{"tid":525301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解每日一到夜晚就發燒？","createTime":"2018-01-10T13:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T13:22:47.000Z","uid":154255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b72d47eae403d70edfb3973b18847ca6652cf5d4","tid":525301,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"點解每日一到夜晚就發燒  <br />\n用緊BRAUN IRT 6520 耳探 去到夜晚就會發燒到37.7~38.1度<br />\n但腋探會36.8~37.0度 <br />\n感冒已經病左1個月 一直都咳同有小小鼻水<br />\n前排勁易頭暈  同埋 個人好累 <br />\n心臟有時會有痛  睇左6,7次醫生<br />\n前排拔左牙  <br />\n兩次睇急診  醫生都話抽過血驗 佢話正常  X光胸又正常  心電圖又正常<br />\n醫生話我可能感冒未清<br />\n<br />\n但上網睇過可能心膜炎/血癌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇有經驗巴打可以講講應該點樣處理好？<br />\n有冇巴打都試過每到夜晚就會發燒"},{"pid":"d4c4a01018a64aa1415f00b90ae07c67edd77049","tid":525301,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"上網睇唔可信<br />\n再做詳細啲檢驗"},{"pid":"e0406e8fc00d0765a66e19a2eb2de0c6d4563707","tid":525301,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"嚴重精神病患者"},{"pid":"44408e1232978040e9e84ce28d296d470effafcf","tid":525301,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:21:06.000Z","msg":"青山等緊你"},{"pid":"5cae1c357398c6c75bec1c2cd9776dd2d7a8de16","tid":525301,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  認真POST<br />\n精神病患者  意思指係我 有嚴重既情緒病 <br />\n焦慮 同 抑鬱"}]}